---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const title = 'About Genfy — Free online generators';
const description = 'Genfy is an independent site of free online generators. Learn about the project, its mission and how it stays free.';
---
<Layout title={title} description={description} lang="en">
  <article>
    <h1>About Genfy</h1>
    <p>
      Genfy is an independent site of free online generators. The goal is simple: when you
      need a small tool — a strong password, an idea for the name of your new company, a
      QR code, a name for your cat — you find it here fast, with no pop-ups, no signups
      and nothing to install.
    </p>

    <h2>Our mission</h2>
    <p>
      The internet is full of "free tools" that end up asking for an email, a subscription,
      or hide their utility behind layers of intrusive advertising. Genfy is built with the
      opposite idea: every generator should be instant, clear and respectful of the user's
      time.
    </p>

    <h2>How does Genfy stay free?</h2>
    <p>
      Genfy is funded with contextual advertising from Google AdSense. That allows us to
      keep all tools free with no strings attached. We don't sell data, there's no hidden
      "premium" subscription, and ads are clearly labeled as such.
    </p>

    <h2>Privacy by design</h2>
    <p>
      Most generators run entirely in your browser: what you type never leaves your device.
      We don't store histories, we don't build user profiles, and we limit cookie usage to
      what is strictly necessary.
    </p>

    <h2>Languages</h2>
    <p>
      Genfy is available in English and Spanish, with plans to add more languages based on
      demand. Versions are not machine translations: each generator is adapted to the
      particularities of the language (names, examples, context).
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      If you have suggestions, found a bug or want to propose a new generator, write to us
      from the <a href="/en/contact">contact page</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>
